    "comment": "The following auxiliary data set is used for product generation: ESA GlobCoverVersion 2.2. PMR data is stratified into groups based on these land-cover classesfor generation of probability density functions. A land mask is also derived fromthese data. Lakes smaller than the 300 m in extent have been removed in theoriginal data. Resampling to 5 km spatial resolution removed water bodies ofextent less than 5 km. Water bodies and permanent snow and ice areas are maskedbased on this dataset. The optical component algorithm needs model surfacetemperature, which is retrieved from ECMWF ERA.",
